# Virtual environment
venv/

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Environment variables
.env

# Alembic cache
*.egg-info/

# IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
```

---

**If your project has multiple microservices**, also add a `.gitignore` at the top level:
```
ecommerce_platform/
│
├── .gitignore          ← top level (covers all services)
├── auth-service/
│   ├── .gitignore      ← service level (optional, more specific)
│   └── ...
├── product-service/
└── order-service/